i must say this is a little nicer than st. elsewhere,'' the fictional inner-city boston hospital featured in the nbc-tv series, loyd observed tuesday as he walked down the corridor at heartland hospital east. ``i think i'll ask them to change the set.''
loyd will star in a 10-minute video to be distributed nationwide in heartland's search for nursing personnel. he took time between takes to shake hands with heartland employees
having him in it will be an attention getter _ something we hope will catch the eye of nurses who might be looking for a position,'' said debi yancer, associate director of patient care services
